headline: Dollar General (NYSE:DG) Expands SNAP EBT Access Through Partnership With DoorDash
summary: Dollar General (NYSE:DG) recently announced a new partnership with DoorDash to introduce SNAP/EBT payment capabilities, significantly increasing online payment acceptance at its stores and potentially improving access for underserved communities. This collaboration likely played a role in the 10% increase in Dollar General's share price over the past month.
